room_title: Escape room "Biohazard" by Roswell Escapes LLC in Roswell
room_description: Twenty years after the Roswell UFO incident, Walker Air Force Base was mysteriously closed. Despite being abandoned, some military personnel and scientific researchers remained to work. Disguised as the new cleaning crew, you sneak into the lab and discover a secure biological research facility. Disaster awaits you and the world if you cannot escape Contamination!
